VED
===

A tiny vi-like editor written in Pascal. Compiles on MS-DOS (Turbo Pascal 7)
and Linux (FreePascal).

Implemented actions
-------------------

  h   Move cursor left
  l   Move cursor right
  j   Move cursor down
  k   Move cursor up
  G   Go to bottom of document
  o   Insert row below and go to insert mode
  x   Delete selected character
  D   Delete to end of line
  i   Insert text
  I   Insert text at beginning of line
  a   Insert text after cursor
  A   Append text at end of line
  J   Concatenate the line below with the current line

Implemented commands
--------------------

  :w   Save file
  :q   Quit without saving
  :wq  Save file and then quit
